name: Richard GALLIPEAU et al. v. Maureen JORDAN

parties: Richard GALLIPEAU et al. v. Maureen JORDAN.

opinions.text:
ORDER
The defendant’s motion to' affirm the judgment of the Superior Court pursuant to Rule 16(g) is denied.
DORIS, J., did not participate.

attorneys: Joseph J. Macioci, Turner C. Scott, Newport, for plaintiffs.
Stephen E. Cicilline, Providence, for defendant.
